rows.label: qst700807_msg0101
rows.name:
It's very admirable that you're
working so seriously, but...

rows.label: qst700807_msg0102
rows.name:
I think you should go and
apologize to the old woman first.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0201
rows.name:
Sorry to interrupt you
while you're working.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0202
rows.name:
But I think conveying your
sincerity to that old woman is
just as important as your labor!

rows.label: qst700807_msg0301
rows.name:
Haha, not a bad hiding spot,
but it won't work on us.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0302
rows.name:
Now, you will go to that old
woman's place, won't you?

rows.label: qst700807_msg0401
rows.name:
...There are still parts of the
Nopon that I don't understand.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0501
rows.name:
Sorry to bother you
while you're working.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0502
rows.name:
But I think that old woman is
also waiting for your words.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0601
rows.name:
Hey!? Why are you working
at the place you ran to!?

rows.label: qst700807_msg0602
rows.name:
Stop slacking off here and hurry up
and go to that old woman's place!

rows.label: qst700807_msg0701
rows.name:
They say to hide a leaf in the
forest, but to think you'd disguise
yourself as a shop employee.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0702
rows.name:
Quite impressive, but since
I found you, I'll have you go
to the old woman's place.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0801
rows.name: Are you really trying to hide?

rows.label: qst700807_msg0802
rows.name:
Well, no matter. Hurry up and
go to that lady's place.

rows.label: qst700807_msg0901
rows.name:
Hmm, as a way of hiding,
it's quite novel, but...

rows.label: qst700807_msg0902
rows.name:
Now that I've found you, I'll have
you go to that lady's place.
